{"tha-ap490:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap490:0.2":"Pamsukulavagga ","tha-ap490:0.3":"Taraniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap490:1.1":"“Atthadassi tu bhagava, ","tha-ap490:1.2":"sayambhu lokanayako; ","tha-ap490:1.3":"Vinata nadiya tiram, ","tha-ap490:1.4":"upagacchi tathagato. ","tha-ap490:2.1":"Udaka abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap490:2.2":"kacchapo varigocaro; ","tha-ap490:2.3":"Buddham taretukamoham, ","tha-ap490:2.4":"upesim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap490:3.1":"‘Abhiruhatu mam buddho, ","tha-ap490:3.2":"atthadassi mahamuni; ","tha-ap490:3.3":"Aham tam tarayissami, ","tha-ap490:3.4":"dukkhassantakaro tuvam’. ","tha-ap490:4.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap490:4.2":"atthadassi mahayaso; ","tha-ap490:4.3":"Abhiruhitva me pitthim, ","tha-ap490:4.4":"atthasi lokanayako. ","tha-ap490:5.1":"Yato sarami attanam, ","tha-ap490:5.2":"yato pattosmi vinnutam; ","tha-ap490:5.3":"Sukham me tadisam natthi, ","tha-ap490:5.4":"phutthe padatale yatha. ","tha-ap490:6.1":"Uttaritvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap490:6.2":"atthadassi mahayaso; ","tha-ap490:6.3":"Naditiramhi thatvana, ","tha-ap490:6.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap490:7.1":"‘Yavata vattate cittam, ","tha-ap490:7.2":"gangasotam taramaham; ","tha-ap490:7.3":"Ayanca kacchapo raja, ","tha-ap490:7.4":"taresi mama pannava. ","tha-ap490:8.1":"Imina buddhataranena, ","tha-ap490:8.2":"mettacittavataya ca; ","tha-ap490:8.3":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap490:8.4":"devaloke ramissati. ","tha-ap490:9.1":"Devaloka idhagantva, ","tha-ap490:9.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap490:9.3":"Ekasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap490:9.4":"kankhasotam tarissati. ","tha-ap490:10.1":"Yathapi bhaddake khette, ","tha-ap490:10.2":"bijam appampi ropitam; ","tha-ap490:10.3":"Sammadhare pavecchante, ","tha-ap490:10.4":"phalam toseti kassakam’. ","tha-ap490:11.1":"Tathevidam buddhakhettam, ","tha-ap490:11.2":"sammasambuddhadesitam; ","tha-ap490:11.3":"Sammadhare pavecchante, ","tha-ap490:11.4":"phalam mam tosayissati. ","tha-ap490:12.1":"Padhanapahitattomhi, ","tha-ap490:12.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap490:12.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap490:12.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap490:13.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap490:13.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap490:13.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap490:13.4":"taranaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap490:14.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap490:14.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap490:14.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap490:15.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap490:15.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap490:15.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap490:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap490:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap490:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap490:17.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma taraniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap490:18.1":"Taraniyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}